<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Dr Reach: I would say it's more of Qabil establishing the alternate CotBG initially, but the AO Council took matters into their own hands and locked up their relics. Rather than posing as CotBG, this alternate CotBG is more of &quot;Foundation in methodology, CotBG in ideology, and with a dose of &quot;To Hell with the masquerade&quot;.</p>
<p>As for the footnotes, I originally have around 15 of them at maximum, However, I opted to cut them down since some reviewers felt it to be disruptive (although the Guidelines for SH format appears to be alright with liberal use of footnotes).</p>
